item.title: Need help portfowarding!
item.dc:creator: @xxDiluted2xx xxDiluted2xx
item.description:
@xxDiluted2xx wrote:

On the start port put 43596.
On the end port put 43596.
I never used netgear, nor no anything about it. I portforwarded differently. But that’s all I can tell you, and that’s all I know for sure. Good luck with the rest.
